| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。馬田康復後，他又再前往艾克寧頓效力至季尾結束<ref name="bbc6474429">{{en}}{{cite news
| title = Accrington retain Martin on loan
| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/a/accrington_stanley/6474429.stm
