}}</ref>，免去了降班至[[英格蘭足球議會全國聯賽|全國聯]]的危機<ref name="lfc155785070501-1152">{{en}}{{cite news| last = Platt| first = Mark| title = Stanley boss hails Reds duo| url = http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/archivedirs/news/2007/may/1/N155785070501-1152.htm| publisher = Liverpool F.C.| date = 2007-05-01| accessdate = 2008-05-30| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080425133134/http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/archivedirs/news/2007/may/1/N155785070501-1152.htm| archivedate = 2008-04-25}}</ref>。

2007年11月6日，他在[[晏菲路球場|晏菲路球場]]對[[比錫達斯體育會|比錫達斯]]的[[2007/08球季歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐聯分組賽]]賽事中擔任後備，球隊最終以8-0的比分大勝對手<ref name="uefa301215">{{en}}{{cite news| title = Liverpool look at Dons goalkeeper| url = http://news.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15105/match=301215/postmatch.html| publisher = UEFA| date = 2003-05-11| accessdate = 2008-05-30}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。2007/08球季，利物浦贏得英超預備組北部聯賽冠軍和英超預備組全國冠軍，馬田亦是其中的一員。2008年5月，他與球會續約至2010年6月<ref name="lfc-profile">{{en}}{{cite news |title=1st team squad profiles: David Martin |url=http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/team/squad/martin/ |publisher=Liverpool F.C. |date=2007-02-28 |accessdate=2008-05-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126020511/http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/team/squad/martin/ |archivedate=2009-11-26 }}</ref>。

2008年8月4日，馬田被利物浦外借至[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]球會[[李斯特城足球會|李斯特城]]，為期6個月<ref name="Martin Makes It Seven">{{en}}{{cite news | title = Leicester sign Liverpool keeper | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/7541457.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2008-08-04 | accessdate = 2008-08-04 | archive-date = 2020-06-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200605204356/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/7541457.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。8月12日，他在主場對[[史托港足球會|史托港]]的賽事中首次代表球會上陣，球隊最終以1-0的比分勝出<ref name="Leicester 1-0 Stockport">{{en}}{{cite news | title = Leicester 1-0 Stockport | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7541907.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2008-08-12 | accessdate = 2008-10-01 | archive-date = 2020-09-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200929132228/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/7541907.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。12月，他在李斯特城的外借期被延長至季尾結束<ref name="David Martin Profile">{{en}}{{cite news |title=David Martin Profile |url=http://www.lcfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10274~29171,00.html |publisher=LCFC.co.uk |date=2009-01-01 |accessdate=209-01-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120218090800/http://www.lcfc.com/page/ProfilesDetail/0%2C%2C10274~29171%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-02-18 }}</ref>。2009年1月30日，上陣23場保持13場不失球的馬田希望正式加盟李斯特城<ref name="Martin eyes permanent Foxes move">{{en}}{{cite news| title = Martin eyes permanent Foxes move| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/7860435.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2009-01-30| accessdate = 2009-01-31| archive-date = 2020-03-27| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200327112903/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leicester_city/7860435.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。他總共上陣了25場聯賽賽事，雖使他協助球隊贏得冠軍並且升班[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]，不過他卻始終未能正式加盟。

利物浦領隊[[拉法埃爾·賓尼迪斯|拉法埃爾·賓尼迪斯]]將馬田列入[[2009/10賽季歐洲聯賽冠軍盃|歐聯分組賽]]28人名單之中<ref>{{en}}[http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N165679090906-1105.htm REDS NAME CHAMPIONS LEAGUE SQUAD] {{Wayback|url=http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N165679090906-1105.htm |date=20091126015351 }}</ref>。

2009年10月16日，他被外借至[[燦美爾足球會|燦美爾]]，為期一個月<ref>{{en}}{{cite news
| last = Hunter
| first = Steve
| title = Goalkeeper crosses the Mersey
| url = http://www.liverpoolfc.tv/news/drilldown/N166098091016-1206.htm
| publisher = [[Liverpool_F.C.|Liverpool F.C.]]
