| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。馬田與球會門將[[勞基·丹尼爾斯|勞基·丹尼爾斯]]競逐正選位置，馬田總共代表燦美爾上陣了3場聯賽賽事。11月26日，馬田被外借至[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]直至12月28日<ref>{{en}}{{cite news | title = Leeds bring in trio on loan deals | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8381293.stm | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2009-11-26 | accessdate = 2009-11-27 | archive-date = 2020-08-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200804142223/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/leeds_united/8381293.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，雖然他的加盟取代了受傷的[[沙恩·希捷士|沙恩·希捷士]]，不過仍需要與[[卡斯柏·安基格倫|卡斯柏·安基格倫]]競逐正選位置。2010年3月10日，[[打比郡足球會|打比郡]]門將{{Link-en|史提芬·拜獲特|Stephen Bywater}}在對[[雷丁足球會|雷丁]]的賽事中傷出，而替補門將{{Link-en|梳爾·甸尼|Saul Deeney}}又於同一場賽事領紅<ref>{{en}}{{cite news| title = Reading   4 - 1   Derby| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8557684.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2010-03-10| accessdate = 2010-03-13| archive-date = 2020-07-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200715165745/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8557684.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>，使馬田被外借至打比郡一個月<ref>{{en}}{{cite news| title = Liverpool keeper David Martin joins Derby County| url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8565340.stm| publisher = BBC Sport| date = 2010-03-12| accessdate = 2010-03-13| archive-date = 2010-03-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100317195326/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/8565340.stm| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2010年5月12日馬田確認於7月1日與利物浦約滿後重返母會[[米尔顿凯恩斯足球俱乐部|米爾頓凱恩斯]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/milton_keynes_dons/8678048.stm |title=Liverpool keeper David Martin joins MK Dons |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-05-12 |accessdate=2010-05-15 |archive-date=2020-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200415083041/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/milton_keynes_dons/8678048.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

